data.name: ENDOBRONCHIAL TUBES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Right and Left Sides

## PERFORMANCE
- Anatomic Tip allowing successful introduction
- High Seal pressure balloon
- Encapsulated radiopaque stripe all along the tube length
- Clear Tube
